# Design System — Calm FemTech

## Theme: "Calm FemTech"
Blue base (#4A90D9) + Pink accents (#F43F68). Soft, trustworthy, feminine.

## Colors — NEVER Hardcode

```typescript
// CORRECT: Use tokens
import { Tokens } from "@/theme/tokens";
import { useThemeColors } from "@/hooks/useTheme";

const bg = isDark ? Tokens.neutral[900] : Tokens.neutral[50];
const accent = Tokens.brand.accent[500];

// WRONG: Never use raw values
const bg = "#FFFFFF";        // NO
const text = "black";        // NO
const pink = "rgba(244,63,104,1)"; // NO
```

## Token Structure (`src/theme/tokens.ts`)
```
Tokens.brand.primary[50-900]    — Blue palette
Tokens.brand.accent[50-900]     — Pink palette
Tokens.brand.secondary[50-900]  — Purple palette
Tokens.brand.teal[50-900]       — Teal palette
Tokens.neutral[0-900]           — Gray scale (0=white, 900=near-black)
```

## Spacing (8pt grid)
```typescript
import { spacing } from "@/theme/tokens";
// spacing.xs=4, spacing.sm=8, spacing.md=12, spacing.lg=16, spacing.xl=24, spacing["2xl"]=32
```

## Dark Mode
Always support both themes:
```typescript
const { isDark } = useTheme();
const bgColor = isDark ? Tokens.neutral[900] : Tokens.neutral[50];
```

## Styling
- Use NativeWind (`className`) with `cn()` helper when possible
- Fallback to `StyleSheet.create()` for complex styles
- Use `radius` tokens for border-radius
- Use `shadows` tokens for elevation

## Typography
```typescript
import { typography } from "@/theme/tokens";
// typography.fontFamily.regular, .medium, .semibold, .bold
```

## Tap Targets
- Minimum 44pt for all interactive elements
- Use padding to increase hit area, not the visual element size
